## Today's pick (2026-05-17)

**Bio-BLIP: A Multimodal Architecture for Transferable Reasoning in Genomic Variant Interpretation** — Gupta, Buendia, Kundaje, Leskovec (Stanford), bioRxiv 10.64898/2026.05.12.724740, v1 posted 2026-05-15.

