- General web / Nature / Science — no fresh agentic-biomedical-AI headline in window

**Why SpatialClaw won:** (1) direct Su Lab fit across agentic AI + KGs + ontologies + data integration + reproducibility; (2) the graph-based persistent memory plus MAR operator is the architectural pattern worth carrying forward — versioned nodes/edges + promotion policy = KG primitives applied to agent memory; (3) memory-only ablation isolates the value of the reasoning bridge rather than just having any memory; (4) end-to-end paper-grade biology demonstration (TNBC, 15 sections, 3 turns); (5) thematically distinct from recent stretch (first persistent-memory-as-graph episode and first deep-skill-library episode in this run); (6) on-recency (v1 posted 2026-05-25).

